> > > about "more interior space " than (posssiblpy said) any car in its
class 
> > > "due to its cab forward design"
> > > 
> > > i started screaming at the TV of course...i tend to do that these
days..
> > > told the TV that hy ol' 69 has more interior space than it, with its
REAL 
> > > cab forward design..and that my 75 has even more, with its total
lasck of 
